import {Table} from 'react-bootstrap'; import {ToDoEntry} from '../model/ToDoEntry'; function List(props: {items: ToDoEntry[], onStatusChange: (user: ToDoEntry) => void}) { const rows = props.items.map((user) => ( {user.vorname} {user.nachname} {user.beschreibung} {user.date.toISOString()} )); return ( {rows}
Vorname Nachname Beschreibung ErstellungsDatum Action
); } export default List;
